    """Build the top-level argument parser with rich help text."""
    description = (
        "Script history & knowledge log CLI for AI agents.\n\n"
        "Use this tool to maintain an append-only history and knowledge base\n"
        "for each script or service in this repository. This helps agents\n"
        "understand why scripts exist, how they evolved, and which caveats or\n"
        "insights apply.\n\n"
        "Related tools:\n"
        "  - tasks: execution backlog and agent coordination.\n"
        "  - findings/fixreport: bug lifecycle from intake to closure.\n"
        "  - hypothesis: falsifiable reasoning and evidence timelines.\n"
        "  - scriptinfo: cross-store timeline + wiki/indexer context.\n\n"
        "Guardrails:\n"
        "  - Exactly one 'init-script' event per script path (enforced).\n"
        "  - Automatic deduplication of identical back-to-back events within\n"
        "    a short time window (configurable via env vars).\n"
